stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Initializing: student calls lab:[id]:init
    Initializing --> WaitingForWorker: no worker capacity available
    WaitingForWorker --> Initializing: worker becomes available (backoff retry)
    Initializing --> Deploying: worker selected, clab:deployLab dispatched
    Deploying --> Failed: partial/total deploy failure
    Failed --> [*]: session row rolled back, worker counters decremented
    Deploying --> Active: all nodes deployed, lab_session_node rows inserted

    Active --> Active: node health/interface updates stream in
    Active --> Active: evaluator check pass/fail transitions stream in
    Active --> Overridden: another tab/device takes over (force connect)
    Overridden --> Active: original tab reconnects and takes back over

    Active --> Submitting: student manually submits OR dueDate BullMQ job fires
    Submitting --> Scored: weighted score computed from lab_session_check rows
    Scored --> Destroying: clab:destroyLab dispatched (tolerant of worker unreachable)
    Destroying --> Ended: containers removed, lab_session_node rows deleted
    Ended --> [*]
